sir"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:29:11.000Z","msg":"good evening sir"},{"pid":"335bb4dcb55736e77e907e16ce5a9aaf88f8df57","tid":1823522,"uid":309595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:31:38.000Z","msg":"其實黃色經濟圈可能真系食緊人血饅頭 但更加在乎系佢食緊嘅同時點樣為呢埸運動付出 唔好任何有關金錢收益就扣人地帽子話人地食人血饅頭只會令更加多想支持嘅人反感 其次如果你要人地張所有收益捐出去 先叫唔系食人血饅頭 米等於提高黃店門檻 黃色經濟圈更加難發展"},{"pid":"c56eafe23f373567961023da6749cdbbc9c3f1d9","tid":1823522,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"一路都唔明就算全世界都剩係食黃店 啲藍店執晒咁又點 會距離五大訴求近咗一步咩？<br />\n成日話咩食黃店係我地唯一可以做到嘅 黃店都唔幫襯仲講咩抗爭 根本就係比班左膠自我感覺良好先發明出嚟"},{"pid":"7a2eb5887471aef02d32da7012c749f55c6ad285","tid":1823522,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc92069f1dcc4d69f9e7323f9ffe8403b341ae1f","tid":1823522,"uid":47834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=cbb02e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again</a><br />\n<br />\n30秒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"告急！！！最後5日，差5萬人簽名，請大家幫手🙏<br />\n<br />\n差5萬1千，截止日期17/1/2020<br />\n(15)聯邦政府應將習近平的女兒從美國驅逐出境<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-shall-expel-ccp-chairman-xi-jinpings-daughter-xi-mingze-united-states\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Ffederal-government-shall-expel-ccp-chairman-xi-jinpings-daughter-xi-mingze-united-states&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=89a6b97d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/federal-government-shall-expel-ccp-chairman-xi-jinpings-daughter-xi-mingze-united-states</a>"},{"pid":"ad006ad09f7bf7ecaaf855b99a012f364b6553d4","tid":1823522,"uid":59305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:36:16.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈最大嘅價值唔係佢創造咗幾多商機比同路人<br />\n係而家佢係社會上面形成嘅氛圍<br />\n令到抗爭可以喺遊行外可以延續 繼而融入生活<br />\n其實呢個經濟圈已經係社會上邊形成到一種壓力比對家<br />\n唔知你又同唔同意呢?<br />\n<br />\n回覆返你個標題<br />\n你講得一啲都冇錯 黃色經濟圈係人血饅頭<br />\n但唔食並唔會顯得你特別高尚<br />\n反而我哋要繼續食 仲要食得津津有味<br />\n咁之前嘅人付出 先至唔會白費<br />\n最好呢個饅頭 食到啲藍店慢慢收皮<br />\n食到有更多嘅黃店 更多嘅鋪頭貼文宣<br />\n更多嘅鋪頭願意表態 咁呢個饅頭先有最大嘅價值"},{"pid":"628f1b2b6c045e2f3c221a1d89a0d542ea6309e2","tid":1823522,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:37:49.000Z","msg":"um..  我覺得你冇講錯，但講漏。 冇錯，呢個黃圈的而且確係令有班人以為食左就等於抗爭左。  但同時你再知，黃圈係不可或缺嘅野，係香港獨立前必須全面做工嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有普選  唯有獨立</span></span>"}]}